{"tid":908672,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好記得當初同你一齊行過嘅人","createTime":"2018-11-19T17:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T18:52:46.000Z","uid":144559,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3aec12bd01e9e4f0edbcc7bd486e5ec5e3e4a4c6","tid":908672,"uid":144559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T17:44:30.000Z","msg":"話我念舊話我on9都好<br />\n<br />\n人越大識到人嘅人越多<br />\n慢慢可能你就會同新一堆朋友好熟<br />\n推哂舊朋友嘅聚會<br />\n<br />\n但問心依家嗰堆好close咩<br />\n應酬你同你擦鞋乜都有<br />\n嗰啲人仲話 喂不如下年一齊去日本旅行<br />\n而你知道呢啲都係吹水<br />\n<br />\n當初陪你長大嗰個朋友<br />\n可能就係默默地做聚會搞手<br />\n而約親你都唔得<br />\n乜柒上莊 同大學朋友上深圳過夜就咩都得<br />\n仲興奮話即興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望大家心入面仲會有中學同學嘅位置<br />\n佢地接觸過最純樸嘅你<br />\n等你迷惘嗰陣可以搵返自己"},{"pid":"3c136cdb5c763a5b7c9f2a415d0f2fa023c71178","tid":908672,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T17:46:21.000Z","msg":"中學 甚至小學既朋友先可以最真最長久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea4d1bb497adb7aa9e99a138f79e5ede8d97734","tid":908672,"uid":170867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c136cdb5c763a5b7c9f2a415d0f2fa023c71178","tid":908672,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T17:46:21.000Z","msg":"中學 甚至小學既朋友先可以最真最長久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T17:48:38.000Z","msg":"大學講利益 交親既都唔係真心"},{"pid":"594bd236ca980cca135fd2661d27f6a69b084cdd","tid":908672,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ea4d1bb497adb7aa9e99a138f79e5ede8d97734","tid":908672,"uid":170867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c136cdb5c763a5b7c9f2a415d0f2fa023c71178","tid":908672,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T17:46:21.000Z","msg":"中學 甚至小學既朋友先可以最真最長久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T17:48:38.000Z","msg":"大學講利益 交親既都唔係真心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T17:50:05.000Z","msg":"我好彩d 都有一兩個間唔中傾下計打下機"},{"pid":"7f14815b5bc89aea4ae4ae45cc3ed8db558dd2b8","tid":908672,"uid":211168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T17:50:44.000Z","msg":"憶起與你做愛跌入了旋風"},{"pid":"d8fa7aba4441d9ff36f661aa6d3ed0bfda8691dd","tid":908672,"uid":92042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T17:51:31.000Z","msg":"但對方已經唔記得自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92129f5014d2c13517d5e3eecd65a47afa47f571","tid":908672,"uid":202011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T18:46:19.000Z","msg":"人地心入面有冇你又係一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094ad796a6060e25e1091aeb2eedd36a1c6e745f","tid":908672,"uid":220174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T18:52:46.000Z","msg":"無忘初衷。<br />\n<br />\n當年大家都交個心出黎做朋友，係最純真最冇垢嘅時候能夠相遇同認識係一種福份。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家能夠好好keep落去，好好珍惜。<br />\n<br />\n有兩個小學都依家嘅好兄弟，就算幾耐無見大家都重係咁friend。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}